agilermi.utility.file

Class RandomAccessServiceAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • agilermi.utility.file.RandomAccessServiceAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Remote, RandomAccessService, java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable

    public class RandomAccessServiceAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements RandomAccessService
    This class is a wrapper for the standard RandomAccessFile instances of the JDK. In fact, The mentioned class does not implement a unique interface that exports all the methods of the implementation. It is useful but not strictly necessary to export the RandomAccessFile instances remotely.
    Author:
    Salvatore Giampa'
